title: Skip James - Devil Got My Woman (1968)
description:
SKIP JAMES - Devil Got My Woman
Vanguard CD 1968

Recorded March, 1966
Performed solo on guitar and/or piano.

Skip was sick but in good musical form. A man out of time. Ghostly.
